            <div class="cs-rich__hyp-badge">Zero Token Drift</div>
            <p class="cs-rich__body-text" style="font-size: var(--tao-typography-size-md); line-height: 1.7;">Because Claude reads token names from Style Dictionary rather than inventing them, every generated surface, text style, and border references a real, versioned token. Theming, dark mode, and brand overrides all work automatically — the AI never hard-codes a hex value or a pixel size.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

